title: Native - Feel Real
typeOfFood: Vegan, Raw, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Fusion
description: Cozy vegan cafe est. Aug 2015 serving mostly raw and healthful meals and sweets. Features green smoothies and juices; granola and fresh fruit on acai or coconut yogurt; big and colorful salads; pancakes and tofu scramble; raw lasagna and raw pizza. Note that the kitchen closes 3pm on weekdays and 4pm on weekends. Access is by a door on street level just back from the corner on Wentworth St - look for it.
